name: Theodorus2
tagline: A new and improved SQLite query tool
body:
Theodorus2
==========

A new and improved SQLite query tool for Windows.

The original version of theodorus is [here](https://code.google.com/p/theodorus/).
This intends to be a complete rewrite though with the same features as before.

An installer for Windows can be found [here](https://github.com/sillyotter/Theodorus2/releases/download/v1.0-alpha/setup.zip)
